ining table might be worth it if lots of family and friends live nearby while a smaller table might fit better with your space and social life if you like having options purchase one with a table leaf so you can accommodate both large and small parties to add a more trendy feel try mismatched chairs or a metal table or go traditional with an allwood set in the end pick what works for your family budget and overall stylemake entertaining easy with a buffet tablewhen a dining room and kitchen are separate going back to the kitchen for seconds can seem like quite a trek instead of forcing guests to make the move bring the food to them by investing in a buffet table with a sideboard you can place all the food in one spot so that guests can conveniently pick at their leisure because its also another flat surface you can use it for decorations candles vases and picture frames toocreate your own home bar stationno good party is complete without a bar but if a custom builtin is out of reach and out of your price range you can still get the same effect by piecing together your own station a bar cart is a great option because it’s portable and can be conveniently squeezed into any corner just stock it with all the necessities — cocktail shaker ice bucket barware and alcohol of your choice — and your guests can just help themselvesdress up your dining room with table linenswhen you’re hosting a party one of the best ways to add character is to pick the right table linens during a formal dinner party nothing says “elegant” more than ivory linen napkins napkin rings and a satin tablecloth or it might not feel quite like christmas without red and green napkins and a lovely christmas tablecloth by owning a wide variety of table linens you will be prepared for everything even your little kid’s messy birthday party besides being above all practical having a variety of napkins and tablecloths is a great way to bring some personality and decor to your table without seeming over the topensure that your dinnerware fits the billas with table linens make sure you have dinnerware that complements a wide variety of events you can store your fancy dishes and glassware in a corner china cabinet if you like and only bring them out for special formal events for a more laidback fingerfood party substitute trendy appetizer plates serving bowls and trays for the good china and traditional platters embed photo open photo in new window pagetype pagebrowseproduct united states united kingdom australia deutschland france россия  italia españa danmark sverige ireland singapore new zealand india company about houzzin the newspress infocareerscontact usterms  privacycopyright  trademark explore houzz buttons  badgesmobile appsadvertisefor professionalssell on houzzwrite a reviewfaqs connect with us houzz blogtwitterfacebookgoogleyoutuberss united kingdom australia deutschland france россия  italia españa danmark sverige ireland singapore new zealand india   houzz inc houzz® the new way to design your home™ dr knoll products inc  canfield  oh  company information products resources my account talk to a db advisor  business directory oh canfield catalog and mailorder houses fitness and sporting goods mail order dr knoll products inc d dr knoll products inc claim this business  newton st unit c canfield oh  get directions   wwwbiowellnet business info founded  incorporated annual revenue  employee count  industries fitness and sporting goods mail order contacts gertrude u fischer contact business your email address subject message send message company summary dr knoll products inc was founded in  dr knoll products inc specializes in fitness and sporting goods mail order verified status unverified address unverified last verified  phone unverified payment method unverified view full report similar businesses nearby our similar businesses nearby shows similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found in their dun  bradstreet credibility review p