ed every two years to projects that preserve modernist architecture in  the first knoll modernism award was given to winfried brenne and franz jaschke of the german firm brenne gesellschaft von architekten for the restoration of the former adgb trade union school building on the outskirts of berlin the school built between  and  was a project of the bauhaus design school the architects were hannes meyer then director of the bauhaus and hans wittwer the  prize went to hubertjan henket and wessel de jonge the founders of docomomo international for the restoration of zonnestraal sanatorium estate in hilversum the netherlands the  prize was given to a consortium of japanese architects and academics for the restoration of the s hizuchi elementary school on shikoku island japan similar companiesedit ergocentric herman miller vitra furniture usm modular furniture lumiy referencesedit  httpwwwknollcomdesignplanmarketfocus  us securities and exchange commission march   knoll inc commission file no  sec us securities and exchange commission retrieved june      national design awards corporate and institutional achievement — knoll cooper–hewitt smithsonian design museum retrieved  march   on december   knoll announced the acquisition of the buffalo new york based datesweiser furniture corporation  our designers knoll retrieved  march    knoll textiles  people  collection of smithsonian cooperhewitt national design museum  architectuul adgb trade union school  available at httparchitectuulcomarchitectureadgbtradeunionschool accessed  november   world monuments  knoll prize for modernism  zonnestraal sanatorium – pdf retrieved  june  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to knoll knoll knoll international world monuments fund  knoll modernism prize  brochure pdf v t e knoll people florence knoll hans knoll products barcelona chair hardoy chair tulip chair wassily chair authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n gnd  sudoc  bnf cbm data ulan  retrieved fr